These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
Sport: golf, baseball
Food: mango, cucumber
1. Food:mango is in an even position##4
2. Food:cucumber == Sport:baseball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Sport   | baseball | golf |
| Food     | cucumber    | mango   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
Nationality: mexican, japanese
City: hannover, edinburgh
1. City:hannover is in an odd position##4
2. Nationality:japanese is on the left of Nationality:mexican##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Nationality   | japanese | mexican        |
| City      | hannover  | edinburgh |

 #################################
 
